#: ../../source/unit/tvoc.rst:3 fc2ce7f994bd456da2a632f1ffdf68c3
msgid "TVOC Unit"
msgstr "TVOC Unit"

#: ../../source/unit/tvoc.rst:7 3cebbe35371d48298d7fbf69c0688afd
msgid ""
"TVOCUnit is a hardware module for measuring Total Volatile Organic "
"Compounds (TVOC) and equivalent CO2 (eCO2). It is based on the SGP30 "
"sensor and communicates via the I2C interface. The class supports "
"configuration and measurement operations."
msgstr ""
"TVOCUnit 是一款用于测量总挥发性有机化合物（TVOC）和等效二氧化碳（eCO2）的硬件模块。它基于 SGP30 传感器，并通过 I2C "
"接口进行通信。该类支持配置和测量操作。"

